---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import quote from "../assets/images/quote-icon.png";
import tommySuharto from "../assets/images/hutomo-mandala-putra.png";
---

<section class="px-[16px] md:px-[64px] lg:px-[80px] py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- LEFT QUOTE -->
    <div class="relative">
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px] md:text-[17px] mb-6">
        <a href="/">PT Bumi Asri Prima Pratama (BAPP)</a> was established with a clear
        commitment to building a structured and resilient fuel supply platform capable
        of supporting Indonesia’s industrial and maritime growth
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px] md:text-[17px] mb-6">
        From the outset, the company focused on operational discipline, supply
        reliability, and long-term partnership development. Over time, BAPP
        strengthened its governance framework, logistics coordination, and
        strategic storage positioning to ensure stable fuel distribution across
        diverse market conditions.
      </p>
      <Image src={quote} alt="quote icon" class="w-8 h-8" />

      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[16px] md:text-[17px] mb-3">
        “Operational integrity and structured management remain the foundation
        of the company’s continued expansion.”
      </p>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <Image
          src={tommySuharto}
          alt="Hutomo Mandala Putra"
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
        />
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hutomo Mandala Putra</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">President Director</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT CARD -->
    <div class="bg-[#018FF5] text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Our Journey</h3>

      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4 text-white/90">
        Founded in 2004, BAPP began as a focused fuel trading and distribution
        operator serving selected industrial clients.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6 text-white/90">
        Through continuous expansion, the company broadened its capabilities
        into marine fuel supply, bunker services, ship-to-ship operations, and
        floating storage infrastructure, strengthening its presence across
        Indonesia’s maritime corridors.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6 text-white/90">
        Today, BAPP operates with integrated supply systems, structured
        governance oversight, and disciplined financial management to maintain
        long-term operational stability.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-[#018FF5] font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
